    <title>LaTeX 入门</title>
    <link href="/2025/05/24/LaTeX/"/>
    <url>/2025/05/24/LaTeX/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>LaTeX 是一个强大的排版系统，尤其适合撰写包含大量数学公式、图表和结构化内容的文档。本文将简要介绍如何使用 LaTeX 编写数学公式以及插入浮动体（图表等）。</p><h2 id="1-基本数学公式"><a href="#1-基本数学公式" class="headerlink" title="1. 基本数学公式"></a>1. 基本数学公式</h2><p>数学公式分为<strong>行内公式</strong>与<strong>块级公式</strong>，分别使用 <code>$...$</code> 与 <code>\[...\]</code> 来编写：</p><p><strong>行内公式：</strong></p><p>例如：$a^2 + b^2 &#x3D; c^2$ 表示勾股定理。</p><p><strong>块级公式：</strong></p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\[</span><br>E = mc<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>2<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\]</span><br>````<br>显示为：<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span><br>E = mc<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>2<br><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span><br><br><span class="hljs-params">##</span> 2. 常见数学符号<br><br>* 上标/下标：<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span>x<span class="hljs-keyword">\_</span>i<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span>x<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>2<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><br>* 分数：<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\frac</span>&#123;a&#125;&#123;b&#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><br>* 根号：<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\sqrt</span>&#123;x&#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span>，<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\sqrt</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\[</span>n]&#123;x&#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><br>* 极限：<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\lim</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\_</span>&#123;x <span class="hljs-keyword">\to</span> 0&#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">\sin</span> x&#125;&#123;x&#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><br>* 积分：<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\int</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\_</span>a<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>b f(x) , dx<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><br>* 求和：<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\sum</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\_</span>&#123;i=1&#125;<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>&#123;n&#125; i<span class="hljs-keyword">\$</span><br><br><span class="hljs-params">##</span> 3. 多行公式（align 环境）<br><br>使用 `align` 可以对齐多行公式：<br><br>```latex<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;align&#125;<br>a <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span>= b + c <span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span><br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span>= d + e<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;align&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>显示为：</p><p>$$<br>\begin{align}<br>a &amp;&#x3D; b + c \<br>&amp;&#x3D; d + e<br>\end{align}<br>$$</p><blockquote><p>需要 <code>\usepackage&#123;amsmath&#125;</code> 支持。</p></blockquote><h2 id="4-插入图片（figure-浮动体）"><a href="#4-插入图片（figure-浮动体）" class="headerlink" title="4. 插入图片（figure 浮动体）"></a>4. 插入图片（figure 浮动体）</h2><p>使用 <code>figure</code> 环境插入图片并添加标题：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;figure&#125;[h]<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\centering</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\includegraphics</span>[width=0.5<span class="hljs-keyword">\textwidth</span>]&#123;example.jpg&#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\caption</span>&#123;示例图片&#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\label</span>&#123;fig:example&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;figure&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>图片引用：如图 \ref{fig:example} 所示。</p><blockquote><p>注意：图片路径应为编译时能找到的相对路径，格式常为 <code>.jpg</code>, <code>.png</code>, <code>.pdf</code>。</p></blockquote><h2 id="5-插入表格（table-浮动体）"><a href="#5-插入表格（table-浮动体）" class="headerlink" title="5. 插入表格（table 浮动体）"></a>5. 插入表格（table 浮动体）</h2><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;table&#125;[h]<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\centering</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\caption</span>&#123;示例表格&#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\label</span>&#123;tab:example&#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;tabular&#125;&#123;|c|c|c|&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\hline</span><br>    A <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> B <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> C <span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\hline</span><br>    1 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 2 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 3 <span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span><br>    4 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 5 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 6 <span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\hline</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;tabular&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;table&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>表格引用：如表 \ref{tab:example} 所示。</p><h2 id="6-小贴士"><a href="#6-小贴士" class="headerlink" title="6. 小贴士"></a>6. 小贴士</h2><ul><li>使用 <code>\text&#123;&#125;</code> 在公式中插入文本，例如：$x &gt; 0 \text{ 时有解}$。</li><li>使用 <code>\left</code> 和 <code>\right</code> 自动调整括号大小，例如：$\left( \frac{a}{b} \right)$。</li><li>控制空格：<code>\quad</code>, <code>\,</code>, <code>\!</code> 等。</li></ul><h2 id="7-编译推荐工具"><a href="#7-编译推荐工具" class="headerlink" title="7. 编译推荐工具"></a>7. 编译推荐工具</h2><ul><li>本地：TeX Live + VSCode（推荐插件 LaTeX Workshop）</li><li>在线：Overleaf（适合协作）</li></ul><hr><p>如果你对 LaTeX 感兴趣，欢迎持续关注后续进阶内容，比如宏包使用、模板配置、自定义命令等！</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
